      <h1 class="h4 mb-3">10. Listen to lifecycle events</h1>
      <div class="tutorial-content mb-4">
        <p>HET dispatches events around fetch and content loading.</p>
        <p>Use these hooks when you need to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>customize the outgoing <code>Request</code></li>
          <li>inspect or replace the <code>Response</code></li>
          <li>intercept content before it is inserted</li>
          <li>react after target, <code>het-select</code>, and <code>het-also</code> replacements finish</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Relevant reference:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="reference/requests#lifecycle-events">Lifecycle events</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

